                    <span class="text-info">MULTI-CLASS PROGRESSION</span>
                </h1>
                <p>Players will be able to train each and every single class without creating a new character. We understand that making a decision early in the game can have a great negative impact on the player if they feel like they have made the wrong decision and lose motivation
                to restart. Therefore you will be able to freely switch between classes by simply speaking with a class trainer in a nearby city or various villages and swap your gear and weapons out for best results. Switching classes
